ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend this course wholeheartedly to another student.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course helped me sharpen my research proposal writing skills.
This course is instrumental for taking the next step in writing up field grants and prepping for the year of field work. It is a necessary part of the curriculum.
The course helped me significantly in sharpening the focus of my dissertation research project and formulating a viable research proposal.
